Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.12,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}暗夜的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:43.86,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘘か夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:43.86,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是夢是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.86,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.86,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(345,330)}カラダ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.86,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自分という心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.22,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.22,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.29,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.29,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:56.05,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:56.05,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連這淚水都能將之奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.17,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.17,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.17,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要將死亡歎作恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.83,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終演を歌う金盞花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.83,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鳴唱終演的金盞花
