Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:13.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靜靜綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}將憎恨
